    //-     li
    //-       h2= kind
    //-       ul: each sk in skset
    //-         li #{sk[0]} #[i= '‚óè'.repeat(sk[1])]

    footer
      ul
        li Robot? Check out #[a(href='https://git.io/vPe71'): code YAML source] of this document.
        li Generated #[code #{_now.format('D MMM Y')}]
      code.kthx :wq
